lead_paragraph: John A. Babarovic, an architect who worked on major airport projects as well as residential architecture, died on Nov. 2 in London, where he lived. He was 69. The cause was complications after heart surgery, his family said.
abstract: John A Babarovic, architect who worked on major airport projects, dies at age 69 (M)
